    SchengenVisaPr= eviousVisa
    PreSchengenVisaHolder
    ORAN 1
    Exclusively for individuals who have never obtained a = Schengen visa or whose Schengen visa was issued before 2020.
    ORAN 2
    Exclusively for individuals whose most recent Schengen = visa was obtained after January 1, 2020, and was valid for a period of six = months or less.
    ORAN 3
    Exclusively for individuals whose most recent Schengen= visa was obtained after January 1, 2020, and was valid for more than six m= onths but less than two years.
    ORAN 4
    Exclusively for individuals whose most recent visa was= obtained after January 1, 2020, and was valid for a period of two years or= more.
    ALG 1
    exclusively for people who have never obtained a Schen= gen visa or for people who obtained a Schengen visa before 2020
    ALG 2
    exclusively for people whose last Schengen visa was ob= tained after 1 January 2020 and was valid for a period of six months or les= s
    ALG 3
    exclusively for people whose last Schengen visa was ob= tained after 1 January 2020 and was valid for more than six months and less= than two years
    ALG 4
    exclusively for people whose last visa was obtained af= ter 1 January 2020 and was valid for a period of two years or more
    Important
    Applicants who choose a category that does not match t= heir visa history will not be accepted at the center, and the service fees = will not be refunded. =20
